title: After the oceania week, Riot gave me skin instead of the champion when i still haven't own Jhin O.o?
body: According to the description of the Oceania week, player will receive an unknown random champion but if they have all the champion, they will instead receive a skin. However, I still haven't own jhin so I really wonder what happened ._.? Any help please?

replies.body: ok thanks for telling me that :/
You have to have a champion pool of 10 champions or more; otherwise, you're given a Mystery Skin!
